name: Matthew Snook
text: I wouldn't feed this to starving kids. You'd be better off with a microwave meal...from a different restaurant. …More

name: JAG Road Soldier
text: This is a joke! My dog can cook better than these guys. Less than subpar food, don’t waste your time and money. Hopefully they’ll be gone soon. Wish I had read the reviews before eating here. Sucksssssssss.

name: Matt C.
text: Horrible service. Two people working and they couldn't find time to take my order, tried twice and as soon as I got the first item out they went back to the kitchen.

text: We got this food deliver and we are so so so disappoint with everything spagettti chicken Alfredo and pepperoni Stromboli .. the spaghetti just had a blob of sauce on it like the Alfredo was dry the Stromboli was wet why I don’t know spent $30 and wasn’t able to eat any of it. Smh
